New and updated recommendations for the treatment of juvenile idiopathic arthritis associated uveitis and idiopathic chronic anterior uveitis.
 An update to the previous 2018 SHARE recommendations for the treatment of children with JIAU with the addition of CAU was created using an evidence-based consensus process. This guideline should help support clinicians to care for children and young people with chronic anterior uveitis.
